Cerahelix, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 11:19 PM ET
Machinery

Company Overview of Cerahelix, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Cerahelix, Inc. designs and manufactures PicoHelix ceramic membrane products to make products from biomass, re-use and recycle resources, and to purify water. It offers single channel elements for lab scale and small pilot scale studies; and multi-channel elements for commercial scale projects. The company also provides filter element housings for individual and multi-element configurations; and sells and leases laboratory test systems for small scale research and development testing needs. It serves treatment, separation, and laboratory applications. The company was founded in 2011 and is based in Orono, Maine.


20 Godfrey DriveOrono, ME 04473United StatesFounded in 2011



